  m_Name: u6_Jellyfish
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  entityName: 
  entitySprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: fa5dfd096c6e61742a7b552d75de9656, type: 3}
  introduction:
  - "Yes\u2026 I must pass through here\u2026."
  actionSpeakFeedback:
  - "I am to join my twin sisters\u2026 we are to meet here\u2026 the Tide has guided
    me\u2026\r"
  - "For years we have been separated\u2026 but now we must\u2026"
  - "Must rejoin the familiar flesh\u2026 our bodies were once one and the same\u2026"
  - "And still they are just like me\u2026"
  - "So many of us\u2026 the Tide wants us all here\u2026"
  - "Just like me\u2026"
  - "...I must\u2026"
  - "I must\u2026"
  actionPokeFeedback:
  - A bizarre gelatinous mass floats in mid-air, drifting slightly with the slow,
    rhythmic motion of its lower ring. Ribbon-like tendrils spread out from the main
    body, dragged this way and that by its idle movement. I touch them, and pain
    radiates from my finger immediately while it merely pulls backwards in response.
  sparedDialogue:
  - "I go forth\u2026"
